  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "Kolpak -1S防暴头盔",
      "en": "Kolpak-1S riot helmet"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "Kolpak",
      "en": "K-1S"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "Kolpak-1S可以保护头部免于到冷兵器穿透伤害，符合特殊防护等级GOST R50744-95。它可以抵抗能量50焦耳以上的冲击且避免造成弹片伤害，同时也能减少上述提到的伤害所造成的动载荷。\n\nKolpak-1防护头盔由联盟委员会推荐，供巡逻部队、交通警察、OMON和其他俄罗斯内务部的特殊部队使用。",
      "en": "Kolpak-1S protects the head from the cold piercing-cutting weapons in a special class of protection GOST R50744-95, from fragmentation with an energy of impact up to 50 J, and also serves to reduce the dynamic loads arising from the above-mentioned means of destruction. Kolpak-1 protective helmets are recommended by the Interdepartmental Commission for equipping units of the patrol service, traffic police, OMON and other special units of the Ministry of Internal Affairs of Russia."
    },
    "weight": 2.9,
    "width": 2,
    "height": 2,
    "rarity": "Common",
    "backgroundColor": "default"
  },
